article.story: CHATTANOOGA, Tenn. -- — Bash Wieland had 26 points in Chattanooga's 76-62 victory against Morehead State on Thursday night. Wieland also added five rebounds and three steals for the Mocs (1-3). Honor Huff scored 13 points while going 4 of 12 from the floor, including 2 for 10 from 3-point range, and 3 for 3 from the line and added eight assists. The Eagles (1-3) were led by Dieonte Miles, who posted 13 points, 11 rebounds and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
